{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1431917, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我说先热", "timestamp": 1618123545, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431921, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不知道，我自己一般是先加的热水", "timestamp": 1618123579, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一次杯子里有半杯凉的，我加了小半杯开水，然后马上就喝，结果把我嘴烫着了。", "timestamp": 1618123650, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431950, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "混匀不知道，但先加开水杯子容易炸", "timestamp": 1618123750, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432071, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我一般先加冷，先加热怕坏杯子", "timestamp": 1618124929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先加热水：\n1. 冷水密度大，后加冷水方便冷热混合\n2. 加冷水能避免先加热水后热水飞溅伤人的情况", "timestamp": 1618126097, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先加热水吧，可以对流", "timestamp": 1618126110, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432203, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 280779, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 热水会浮在上面 不是很快就能混合均匀\n", "timestamp": 1618126149, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 280779, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "问各位聪明的童鞋一个问题，想要兑一杯温水，是先加热水还是先加冷水更容易混匀", "timestamp": 1618123526, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618126147,